When in Photoshop chose: Print size (or similiar) and enlarge to 200 % and put in papersheet "A2" size if optional. Then you&#039;ll have the right size of it. If you encounter problem open the files try different types of imageprogrames. 
Some files are somewhat corrupted and the doesn&#039;t work in Photoshop 5.5 but in later versions.
About one third of the files are disorderly
I packed them in a .rar beacause of the corrupted files. 
Some files may be missing.
